1. *Car* je vozio brzo auto. (The *driver* was driving a fast car.)
2. *Carstvo* Rimsko je trajalo mnogo vekova. (The Roman *Empire* lasted for many centuries.)
3. Njegov otac je bio *carski* savetnik. (His father was an *imperial* advisor.)
4. Nemački *kancelar* je posetio Srbiju. (The German *chancellor* visited Serbia.)
5. *Carica* je bila veoma lepa žena. (The *empress* was a very beautiful woman.)
6. *Carinski* službenici su pregledali prtljag. (The *customs* officials inspected the luggage.)
7. Stari *car* je voleo da se šeta po parku. (The old *tsar* liked to take walks in the park.)
8. *Carski* dvor je bio izuzetno raskošan. (The *imperial* court was extremely luxurious.)
9. U ovoj zemlji se ne plaća *carina*. (There is no *customs duty* in this country.)
10. Ruski *car* je abdicirao tokom Revolucije 1917. (The Russian *tsar* abdicated during the Revolution of 1917.)